# Project Memory - ThriveWithSurabhi

## About the Website
This website is about **Surabhi's nutrition coaching**. Surabhi is an **ACE certified nutrition coach**. She was a software engineer and then pivoted to fitness. She specializes in working with **busy women who want to get fit and lose weight**.

## Purpose & Goals
- This website is meant to represent Surabhi as the **go-to expert** for people looking to get fit and lose weight.
- The website should **resonate with users** and the ultimate goal is to **drive client conversions**.

## Design Priority
- **Mobile-first**: Most users will be accessing the website on mobile, so it must be **optimized for a mobile viewing experience first**.
